(6, 'Appliances', 'Furniture', 'TV Showcase', 'Perfect Homes', '7,499', '\r\nUnit Material Subtype: Particle Board\r\nW x H x D: 143.25 cm x 131.57 cm x 39.624 cm (4 ft 8 in x 4 ft 3 in x 1 ft 3 in)\r\nIdeal TV Size: 39 inch\r\nNumber of Drawers: 2, Number of Open Shelves: 6\r\nKnock Down - Delivered in non-assembled pieces, installation by service partner', 'This TV unit is made of 100% safe European Standard Particle Board Engineered wood, with reduced formaldehyde emissions.', 'http://fkrt.it/b4YVE2NNNN', 'TV Showcase', '24-04-2018-15245838321.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245838322.jpg', '', '2018-04-24'),
(7, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'Sony 80 cm (32 inches) Bravia KLV-32R302E HD Ready LED TV', 'sony', '22,999', '2 x 5 W Speaker Output Optimal sound\r\n1366 x 768 HD Ready - Great picture quality\r\n100 Hz : Blur free picture, Smoother movements in videos\r\n2 x HDMI : For set top box and consoles\r\n1 x USB : Get content from USB drives', 'It is a great TV from sony.\r\nPros.\r\n1.great picture quality.\r\n2.great sound quality.\r\n3.colour depth, contrast and brightness etc.. are amazing\r\n4.many great features like fm, picture frame mode, etc....', 'http://fkrt.it/3w0FH2NNNN', 'tv', '24-04-2018-15245899461.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245899462.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245899463.jpeg', '2018-04-24'),
(8, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'Sony Bravia 72.4cm', 'sony', '19,499', '20 W Speaker Output : Rich, powerful sound\r\n1366 x 768 HD Ready - Great picture quality\r\n2 x HDMI : For set top box and consoles\r\n1 x USB : Get content from USB drives', 'With the Sony BRAVIA LED TV at home, you can experience better TV-viewing as it offers a better picture clarity with a glitch-free audio.\r\nClear Resolution Enhancer\r\nEvery scene will look extravagant on this TVâ€™s 72.4 cm (29) screen, thanks to its Clear Resolution Enhancer which upscales low-resolution images and reduces noise. The 1366x768 resolution along with 178-degree viewing angle gives you an immersive entertainment experience.\r\nMulti-format USB\r\nHave some interesting movies, old and ne', 'http://fkrt.it/3wv0L2NNNN', 'sony tv 72 inches', '24-04-2018-15245904181.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245904182.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245904183.jpg', '2018-04-24'),
(9, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'Sony Bravia 80cm', 'sony', '27,999', '8 W x 2 Speaker Output : For good-quality TV sound\r\n1366 x 768 HD Ready - Great picture quality\r\n200 Hz : Blur free picture, Smoother movements in videos\r\n2 x HDMI : For set top box and consoles\r\n2 x USB : Easily connect your digital camera, camcorder or USB device', '\r\nSee more, hear more, and feel more when you invest in this Sony HD Ready Smart LED TV. Built with an effective picture processing engine, you can enjoy your favourite action movies, TV shows, and sports in high-quality. The Smart feature lets you browse your favourite social media sites and watch YouTube videos from the comfort of your couch.', 'http://fkrt.it/pBYmRLuuuN', 'tv', '24-04-2018-15245906591.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245906592.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245906593.jpg', '2018-04-24'),
(10, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'Sony 101.6cm', 'sony', '42,999', '10 W Speaker Output\r\n1920 x 1080 Full HD - Watch Blu-ray movies at their highest level of detail\r\n100 Hz : Blur free picture, Smoother movements in videos\r\n2 x HDMI : For set top box and consoles\r\n1 x USB : Get content from USB drives', 'Movie nights, catching live telecasts of sports events, or jamming to your favorite songs are enhanced on this 102 cm (40) Full-HD LED TV. This TV is designed to highlight the brilliance of image colors, and has features which you can customize to suit your viewing needs.\r\nHigh-definition Entertainment\r\nThis Full-HD LED TV lets you enjoy clear and detailed images across all your entertainment. From Blu-ray discs to content stored on your smartphone, you can now re-watch classic movies or catch t', 'http://fkrt.it/3eC4j2NNNN', 'sony 101.6cm', '24-04-2018-15245921791.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245921792.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245921793.jpg', '2018-04-24'),
(11, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'Sony 101.4cm (40 inch)', 'sony', '47,100', '30 W Speaker Output\r\n1920 x 1080 Full HD - Watch Blu-ray movies at their highest level of detail\r\n200 Hz : Blur free picture, Smoother movements in videos\r\n2 x HDMI : For set top box and consoles\r\n2 x USB : Easily connect your digital camera, camcorder or USB device', 'Enjoy entertainment king-sized on this Sony Full HD TVâ€™s wide 101.6 cm (40) screen. Itâ€™s not just about its size, this TV has specially designed features like ClearAudio+ and 3 speakers with Dolby Digital Plus that deliver quality picture and sound.\r\nX-Reality PRO lets you be a part of the movies you watch on this television by upscaling every 1920x1080 pixel in this TV to give you thrilling picture clarity. It boosts color, contrast, and sharpness and dramatically reduces picture noise so y', 'http://fkrt.it/3R8~U2NNNN', 'sony tv 101.4cm (40 inch)', '24-04-2018-15245924611.jpeg', '24-04-2018-15245924612.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245924613.jpg', '2018-04-24'),
(12, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'Sony BRAVIA X7002E Series 138.8cm', 'sony', '99,999', '20 W Speaker Output\r\n3840 x 2160 Ultra HD - 4X resolution of Full HD- More depth in every picture\r\n200 Hz : Blur free picture, Smoother movements in videos\r\n3 x HDMI : For set top box, consoles and Blu-ray players\r\n3 x USB : Easily connect your digital camera, camcorder or USB device', 'Bring home a Sony BRAVIA LED Smart TV and experience amazing 4K picture quality with impressive contrast, brightness and a High Dynamic Range. 4K HDR technology improves the clarity of previously hi\r\nEnjoy HDR Gaming with PlayStation\r\nSony 4K HDR TVs are perfect for gamers as they are compatible with the PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 4 Pro consoles. Experience vibrant textures and vivid colours with a fun-filled gaming experience.dden dark shadows and sunlit areas, making entertainment more life', 'http://fkrt.it/3tqv02NNNN', 'sony 138.8cm (5inch)', '24-04-2018-15245934581.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245934582.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245934583.jpeg', '2018-04-24'),
(13, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'KLV-49W672E', 'sony', '58,900', '30 W Speaker Output\r\n1920 x 1080 Full HD - Watch Blu-ray movies at their highest level of detail\r\n200 Hz : Blur free picture, Smoother movements in videos\r\n2 x HDMI : For set top box and consoles\r\n2 x USB : Easily connect your digital camera, camcorder or USB device', 'With features like X-Reality PRO which boosts image color, brightness, and contrast, and built-in woofer which delivers deeps bass riffs and powerful vocals so you can enjoy an immersive TV-viewing experience, this smart TV from Sony is a great source of entertainment. Thatâ€™s not it. Its remote has a dedicated button that gives you direct access to Netflix and YouTube!\r\nX-Reality PRO upscales images displayed on this TV. It boosts color, contrast, and sharpness and dramatically reduces noise s', 'http://fkrt.it/phntRLuuuN', 'sony 123.2 cm (49 inch)', '24-04-2018-15245938131.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245938132.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245938133.jpg', '2018-04-24'),
(14, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'KLV-43W772Es', 'sony', '54,999', '30 W Speaker Output\r\n1920 x 1080 Full HD - Watch Blu-ray movies at their highest level of detail\r\n200 Hz : Blur free picture, Smoother movements in videos\r\n2 x HDMI : For set top box and consoles\r\n2 x USB : Easily connect your digital camera, camcorder or USB device', '', 'http://fkrt.it/3ylji2NNNN', 'sony tv', '24-04-2018-15245944381.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245944382.jpg', '24-04-2018-15245944383.jpg', '2018-04-24'),
(15, 'Electronics', 'Speakers', 'Philips Multimedia Speakers', 'philips', '979.00', '3W RMS total output power\r\nBass Reflex Speakers deliver deep and powerful bass\r\nWell damped driver reduces vibration and sound distortion', '', 'https://amzn.to/2Hq8eQK', 'speker', '25-04-2018-15246729641.jpg', '25-04-2018-15246729642.jpg', '25-04-2018-15246729643.jpg', '2018-04-25'),
(16, 'Appliances', 'Air Conditioner', 'Voltas 1 Ton 3 Star', 'Voltas ', '26,799.00', 'Energy Rating: 3 Star (2018). Note that as per Bureau of Energy Efficiency (BEE), there is a 2 point energy rating drop in 2018 for non-inverter split ACs. E.g. a 2017 5 star non-inverter split AC will become 3 star in 2018.\r\nType: Non Inverter Split AC\r\n1 Ton Capacity: Suitable for small sized rooms (< = 120 sq ft)\r\nWarranty: 1 year warranty on product and 5 years warranty on compressor\r\nCondenser Type: Copper for best in class, energy efficient cooling with easy maintenance\r\nSpecial features: ', '1. Avail 5 years of product warranty (1 plus additional 4) on all Voltas ACs including Split and Window ACs for orders made till 31st May â€™18. Please refer T&C to avail this offer > Learn more\r\n\r\n2. Avail No Cost EMI on all major credit cards on the purchase of this product from Seller Cloudtail India. Checkout with this item only. Learn more\r\n\r\nNeed help buying the right AC? Let us help you. Know more', 'https://amzn.to/2vL9KqT', 'ac', '25-04-2018-15246740511.jpg', '25-04-2018-15246740512.jpg', '25-04-2018-15246740513.jpg', '2018-04-25'),
(17, 'Women', 'Women Clothing', 'Nirja Creation Cotton Silk Saree With Blouse Piece', 'Nirja Creation', '1099', 'Premium Quality Superb Saree With Blouse Piece.\r\nSaree Fabric -Cotton Silk, Blouse Fabric :- Cotton Silk, Banarasi Saree.`\r\nMeasurement :- Saree Length - 5.5 Mtr, Blouse Length - 0.80 Mtr.\r\nWash Care :- Dry Clean Or Hand Wash In Cold Water', '', 'https://goo.gl/uv7wv8', 'saree', '26-04-2018-15247398541.jpg', '26-04-2018-15247398542.jpg', '26-04-2018-15247398543.jpg', '2018-04-26'),
(18, 'Electronics', 'TVs', 'Videocon 55cm (22 inch) HD Ready LED TV  (IVC 22F02T / IVC22F02A/ IVC22F29A)', 'videocon', '9,499', '16 W Speaker Output\r\n1366 x 768 HD Ready - Great picture quality\r\n60 Hz : Standard refresh rate for blur-free picture quality\r\n1 x HDMI\r\n1 x USB : Get content from USB drives', 'To avoid any physical damage to the product while unboxing, please ensure that only an authorised Flipkart delivery/service executive or brand personnel opens the packaging.', 'http://fkrt.it/EerfTKNNNN', 'videocon 22 inch tv', '06-05-2018-15255532101.jpg', '06-05-2018-15255532102.jpg', '', '2018-05-06'),
(19, 'Appliances', 'Air Conditioner', 'Carrier 1.5 Ton 3 Star BEE Rating 2018 Window AC - White', 'carrier', '26,990', '1.5 Ton\r\n3 Star : For energy savings upto 15% (compared to Non-Inverter 1 Star)\r\nAuto Restart: No need to manually reset the settings post power-cut\r\nCopper : Energy efficient, best in class cooling with easy maintenance.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/n8mKQKNNNN', 'A/c, Air conditioner, 1.5 Ton Ac, carrier a/c', '07-05-2018-15256827071.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256827072.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256827073.jpg', '2018-05-07'),
(20, 'Appliances', 'Air Conditioner', 'Carrier 1.5 Ton 2 Star BEE Rating 2018 Split AC - White', 'carrier', '33,990', '1.5 Ton\r\n2 Star : For energy savings upto 5% (compared to Non-Inverter 1 Star)\r\nAuto Restart: No need to manually reset the settings post power-cut\r\nCopper : Energy efficient, best in class cooling with easy maintenance.\r\nSleep Mode: Auto-adjusts the temperature to ensure comfort during your sleep', 'Effective 1st of Jan, 2018, BEE has enforced a downgrade of 2 stars for Fixed Speed Split ACs. For e.g., a 5-star-rated Split AC, as per BEE norms in 2017, is a 3-star from 2018 (Change Not Applicable to Inverter & Window ACs). For a given star rating, a Fixed Speed AC and an Inverter AC will have similar energy-efficiency (ISEER).', 'http://fkrt.it/nLGV0KNNNN', 'A/c, Air conditioner, 1.5 Ton Ac, carrier a/c', '07-05-2018-15256843261.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256843262.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256843263.jpg', '2018-05-07'),
(21, 'Appliances', 'Air Conditioner', 'Carrier 1.5 Ton 3 Star BEE Rating 2018 Inverter AC - White  ', 'carrier', '38,990', '1.5 Ton\r\n3 Star : For energy savings upto 15% (compared to Non-Inverter 1 Star)\r\nAuto Restart: No need to manually reset the settings post power-cut\r\nCopper : Energy efficient, best in class cooling with easy maintenance.\r\nSleep Mode: Auto-adjusts the temperature to ensure comfort during your sleep', 'End a tiring day of being outdoors in the heat, on a good note by coming home to a cool space. This split AC from Carrier, with its different modes, aims to make your summers easy and breezy.', 'http://fkrt.it/np~hMKNNNN', 'carrier 1.5 ton A/c', '07-05-2018-15256845911.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256845912.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256845913.jpg', '2018-05-07'),
(22, 'Appliances', 'Air Conditioner', 'Carrier 1.5 Ton 3 Star BEE Rating 2018 Split AC - White ', 'carrier', '32,490', '1.5 Ton\r\n3 Star : For energy savings upto 15% (compared to Non-Inverter 1 Star)\r\nAuto Restart: No need to manually reset the settings post power-cut\r\nCopper : Energy efficient, best in class cooling with easy maintenance.\r\nSleep Mode: Auto-adjusts the temperature to ensure comfort during your sleep', 'Effective 1st of Jan, 2018, BEE has enforced a downgrade of 2 stars for Fixed Speed Split ACs. For e.g., a 5-star-rated Split AC, as per BEE norms in 2017, is a 3-star from 2018 (Change Not Applicable to Inverter & Window ACs). For a given star rating, a Fixed Speed AC and an Inverter AC will have similar energy-efficiency (ISEER).', 'http://fkrt.it/KMqrVnuuuN', 'A/c, Air conditioner, 1.5 Ton Ac, carrier a/c', '07-05-2018-15256849021.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256849022.jpg', '07-05-2018-15256849023.jpg', '2018-05-07'),
