(182, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Billion 1000 W Non-stick Compact XR128 Dry Iron  (White and Black)', 'billion', '325.00', 'Bring home the Billion Compact Dry Iron for a uniform and creaseless ironing experience. It comes with a thermal fuse that protects it from overheating, while the 360-degree swivel cord makes for easy and free movement of the iron.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/nIFGUKNNNN', 'iron box, Billion 1000 W Non-stick Compact XR128 Dry Iron  (White and Black)', '16-05-2018-15264912191.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264912192.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264912193.jpg', '2018-05-16'),
(183, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Flipkart SmartBuy Electric Kettle  (1.5 L, Black)', 'flipkart', '599.00', 'Boil water in a matter of minutes for baby food or make a steaming cup of fragrant tea with the 1.5L Flipkart SmartBuy electric kettle. Beautifully crafted and featuring a stainless-steel body, this kettle is perfect for your kitchen or office pantry. It is also lightweight and compact, making it easy to carry. To top it off, it also comes with the best in class safety features, making it safe to use.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/KSqISnuuuN', 'electric kettle, Flipkart SmartBuy Electric Kettle ', '16-05-2018-15264913681.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264913682.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264913683.jpg', '2018-05-16'),
(184, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Bajaj DX 2 L/W Dry Iron  (Grey)', 'bajaj', '499.00', '\r\nIroning is no more a tedious job with this dry iron from Bajaj. Equipped with this iron, you donâ€™t need to worry about wrinkled clothes, as it will smoothen them out and make them look crisp in no time.\r\n\r\nLightweight\r\n\r\nUnlike other irons, this one is lightweight for ease of convenience for you while using it. Even if you have a lot of clothes to iron, your hand will not pain from the weight of this iron as it is lightweight.\r\n\r\nNon-stick coated soleplate\r\n\r\nThe soleplate features a non-stick coating to prevent clothes from sticking onto it. \r\n\r\nAdjustable thermostat control\r\n\r\nThe thermostat control will help you set the temperature level according to different types of fabric.\r\n\r\nSwivel cord\r\n\r\nThe swivel cord offers convenience in moving the iron over the clothes without any discomfort.\r\n\r\nThermal fuse\r\n\r\nIt automatically disconnects the power to the heating element when any electrical malfunction occurs. This prevents the temperature from rising which might result in a short circuit.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/nID3WKNNNN', 'iron, Bajaj DX 2 L/W Dry Iron  (Grey)', '16-05-2018-15264916821.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264916822.jpg', '', '2018-05-16'),
(185, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'TP Magic Dry Iron', 'TP', '299.00', 'Magic Dry IronTemperature setting allows you to select and check temperature setting easily and accurately.The Power cord can be set up on either side to allow easy ironing for right or left-hand operation.Aluminum alloy sole plate PTFE coated lets the iron glide over all types of fabrics without sticking or scorching.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/nfkF1KNNNN', 'iron, dry iron, TP Magic Dry Iron', '16-05-2018-15264947601.jpg', '', '', '2018-05-16'),
(186, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Usha EI 1602 Dry Iron ', 'usha', '589.00', 'Nothing can boost your confidence better than wearing neatly pressed clean clothes. Now iron your clothes right at your home anytime you want with this dry iron from Usha. Featuring an ergonomically designed, lightweight body and many amazing features, this dry iron is easy to use and quite handy.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/nfsUDKNNNN', 'iron, Usha EI 1602 Dry Iron', '16-05-2018-15264948941.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264948942.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264948943.jpg', '2018-05-16'),
(187, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Billion 1100 W Non-stick Extra-power XR126 Dry Iron  ', 'billion', '349.00', 'Indians, arguably, have the most varied collection of outfits. We love to wear cotton T-shirts and kurtas, but we equally love our silk sarees, woollen suits and chiffon dresses. We also iron most of our clothes at home, only occasionally relying on professional help. Which is why, we need irons at home. This Billion 1100 W Non-stick, ExtraPower XR126 Dry Iron features a Teflon coating. It has been designed for quick and easy ironing to give your clothes the perfect crisp and crease-less finish. This made-for-India iron is stick-resistant. It glides smoothly over all types of fabric without sticking to them.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/K6S2snuuuN', 'iron, Billion 1100 W Non-stick Extra-power XR126 Dry Iron', '16-05-2018-15264950101.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264950102.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264950103.jpg', '2018-05-16'),
(188, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Bajaj DX6 Dry Iron  (White)', 'bajaj', '549.00', 'You donâ€™t need to wear fancy clothes from high-end brands to look presentable. Wearing neatly ironed clothes is enough to look your best. Get this 1000 W Bajaj dry iron and remove all those stubborn creases and wrinkles off your clothes.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/nGVZWKNNNN', 'iron, Bajaj DX6 Dry Iron  (White)', '16-05-2018-15264951221.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264951222.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264951223.jpg', '2018-05-16'),
(189, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Billion 1000 W Non-stick Compact XR128 Dry Iron  (White and Black)', 'Billion ', '325.00', '\r\nKeep your clothes looking new with this Non-stick Compact dry iron from Billion. Its two layer of American Heritage Coating Plate ensures a smooth gliding experience while the well-designed grip handle ensures a secure and comfortable grip.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/norHnKNNNN', 'iron, Billion 1000 W Non-stick Compact XR128 Dry Iron  (White and Black)', '16-05-2018-15264952491.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264952492.jpg', '16-05-2018-15264952493.jpg', '2018-05-16'),
(190, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Philips GC1905 Steam Iron, 1440 W  (White and blue)', 'Philips', '1,299', 'Save time on household chores while you use Philips GC1905 iron which is built to perfection so as to give you a quick ironing experience.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/KWZ~EnuuuN', 'iron, Philips GC1905 Steam Iron, 1440 W  (W)', '17-05-2018-15264955141.jpg', '17-05-2018-15264955142.jpg', '17-05-2018-15264955143.jpg', '2018-05-17'),
