(196, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Philips GC 181 Dry Iron  (Black)', 'philips', '1,315.00', '\r\nA crisp and nicely pressed shirt will always help you stand out from the crowd and will garner appraising looks. So build the habit of wearing wrinkle-free clothes every day with the help of this Philips dry iron.\r\n\r\nClassic and Durable Design\r\n\r\nThis dry iron has a classic design with a rotating knob right under the handle and a heavy soleplate that aides in removing the creases easily. The soleplate is also coated with Black American heritage coating that allows you to glide the appliances smoothly on your fabric.\r\n\r\nFaster Heating\r\n\r\nThis dry iron operates on around 1000 watts of energy and ensures faster heating. Another best thing about this iron is that it distributes the heat uniformly across the soleplate, making it easier for you to press your clothes at one go.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/nHPGsKNNNN', 'iron, Philips GC 181 Dry Iron  (Black)', '17-05-2018-15264975251.jpg', '17-05-2018-15264975252.jpg', '17-05-2018-15264975253.jpg', '2018-05-17'),
(197, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Billion 1000 W Non-stick Compact XR127 Dry Iron  (White and Sky Blue)', 'billion', '349.00', 'Bring home the Billion Compact XR127 Dry Iron for a uniform and creaseless ironing experience. It comes with a thermal fuse that protects it from overheating, while the 360-degree swivel cord makes for easy and free movement of the iron.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/K7qLwnuuuN', 'iron, Billion 1000 W Non-stick Compact XR127 Dry Iron  (White and Sky Blue)', '17-05-2018-15264976371.jpg', '17-05-2018-15264976372.jpg', '17-05-2018-15264976373.jpg', '2018-05-17'),
(198, 'Appliances', 'Appliances', 'Impex IB 15 Dry Iron  (White)', 'Impex', '1,599.00', 'Heavy weight comfortable iron box with Gold plate sole plate. This heavy weight Iron box has over heat Fuse protection(270Â°C) Pilot lamp and Automatic Thermoslate.', '', 'http://fkrt.it/KWLCGnuuuN', 'iron, Impex IB 15 Dry Iron  (White)', '17-05-2018-15264977611.jpg', '17-05-2018-15264977612.jpg', '', '2018-05-17'),
