(626, 'Men', 'Men Wallets', 'Total Effects Cleanser  (100 g)', 'Olay ', '223.00', '<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">The Olay Story</strong></div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\nA brainchild of a chemist, Olay was born out of love and was Graham Wulffâ€™s gift to his doting wife. Graham wanted to create a new beauty product that would leave his wifeâ€™s skin nourished and moisturized without leaving a greasy feel. Graham and Dinah started an extensive research and finally created the legendary Oil of Olay Beauty Fluid.</div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\nToday, Olay is a well-known and trusted brand that promises the dainty ladies healthy and beautiful skin. Olay delivers products that are safe for its customers by ensuring that each product manufactured undergoes a thorough quality test. Celebrate beauty and pamper your skin with Olay.</div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Foaming Cleanser</strong></div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px;">\r\nEnsuring 7 cleansing benefits in one go, this Total Effects 7 in 1 Foaming Cleanser from Olay gently washes away dirt and other impurities on your skin to give your face a fresh and youthful glow. This cleanser is ideal for both men and women with any skin tone.</div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Claim</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\nTotal Effects 7 in 1 Foaming Cleanser not only washes away dirt and make up impurities but also removes excess oil on your face.</div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Features and Benefits</strong></div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px;">\r\n- Being gently on your skin, this cleanser removes impurities without over drying your skin.<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />- This cleanser lifts dead skin cells from the surface to give you soft and supple skin.<br style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />- Being non-comedogenic, this cleanser removes excess oil without stripping your skin of necessary moisture.</div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Directions</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\nSqueeze a small amount of this cleanser on your hand, mix it with water and work into rich lather. Massage gently on your face and neck for some time and rinse thoroughly with water.</div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">Ingredients</strong></div>\r\n<div style="background-color: white; box-sizing: border-box; color: #212121; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">\r\nThe composition of this cream contains water, glycerin, myristic acid, stearic acid, palmitic acid, sodium lauroyl sarcosinate, potassium hydroxide and other chemicals with a touch of fragrance.</div>', '', 'http://fkrt.it/2t!Ck2NNNN', 'men Total Effects Cleanser', '04-06-2018-15280564571.jpg', '04-06-2018-15280564572.jpg', '04-06-2018-15280564573.jpg', '2018-06-04'),
